# Deep Review — Event-Ticketing-Platform
> Reviewed: April 7, 2026 | Scope: Full project planning layer (no source code exists yet)

---

## 1. Overall Assessment

This is an exceptionally well-prepared planning layer for a production-grade Java/Spring Boot system. The level of pre-implementation design — covering concurrency safety, state machine correctness, payment idempotency, and distributed systems hygiene — is rare for a solo engineering project. The dual-document overlay pattern (original plan + `Phase1A_Adjustments_and_Fixes.md`) is particularly mature.

**Verdict:** The plan is execution-ready. The gaps identified below are real but none are blockers for Day 1. They range from a critical omission in the constitution, to minor inconsistencies between documents.

---

